    {
      "chinese": "以前阿美族人生活非常不容易，種玉米、稻田沒有發展，連地瓜都吃不到。小孩唸書繳不起學費，為了家庭生計，只好到台北礦坑來工作。",
      "ab": "Itiya ho ko Pangcah/’Amis a tamdaw, caayay kafangcal ko ’orip, paloma to ’ariray, panay, awaay ko kalomahadan, o konga to awaay a makaen, o payci to awaay ko sapitilid no kaemangay. Sakanga’ayaw no ’orip saka tayra sanay to i Taypak a misikitang.",
