    {
      "chinese": "挖礦的工作非常艱辛又危險，坑內常常只能容許一個人平躺或側躺地挖煤礦，像蟲一樣在地底鑽，室內溫度平均大概都有三﹑四十度，只好大量喝水以降低身體的熱量；而中午吃飯時便當已經臭酸了。工作完出坑時，全身黑漆漆，只有牙齒是白色的。",
      "ab": "O misikitangay a tayal tadamarorayay o katalawan a tayal, itini i tepong anca cacay ko tamdaw, ti’enang, tokinil sa a misikitang, mahecad to o fao’ a mimokmok i sasera, maedeng sepatay polo’ ira ko tolo ko fa’edet i laloma’, sahonihoni sa a minanom mifasaw to fa’edet no tatirengan, malahok sato ’angliw to ko patafoan. Masadak sato nai tepong hato kohetingay a tamdaw, o wadis to ko kohecalay.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2020/12/29/1157b03c64072655b2490a18963fae1a.wav",
